page.title: 18A NASSINGTON GIRL'S DAY.
page.content: Today I got out of bed and had some Weetabix for breakfast.I got dressed had to get my coat and bag,got in the car and came to school. We had the register and I went and did my maths and then a painting.Soon it was lunch time.We had chips and beans. Then it was playtime.We came in at 1.20 and had register and worked on the computer.Soon we got ready for athletics at the playing field with lots of other local schools.We did lots of running,jumping and throwing to get a 3 A's award. When we got back mummy came to get me and I went in to watch T.V.Then I went to play and came in to have tea.I went out to play until 7.00pm.when we came in and got ready for bed.I read to mummy and got into bed.I read for a long time and then I went to sleep.
